  "description": "Casino Royal features two gambling games: Roulette and Pontoon (blackjack). <br><br>Roulette is played by up to 6 people. When joining the table each player is given £500 worth in chips they must then use to place bets on the table, trying to predict which numbers will be produced by the roulette wheel. <br><br>Pontoon is played alone against the bank. The player starts with a capital of £100 and must aim, when adding the value of the cards in their hands, to get a count of 21, or as near as possible of 21, without going over. <br><br>Both games can take advantage of the Currah Microspeech extension to provide optional digitized sound effects.",
